Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:41.73,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}囚困在从空隙中溢出的阳光 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:44.29,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}白日梦里的小路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.55,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}走着 走着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:51.96,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}加速的引力 反复的动力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.45,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}我全心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:59.83,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}不要分离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:02.43,opn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\be35}如此牵引着我
