Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.48,0:01:43.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 破坏了约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.56,0:02:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好了 你醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了 已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没剪断呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那个 好像是你记忆的片段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.16,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人 之前也对你… 不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.66,0:02:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剪女孩的头发就是犯罪 犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论失去记忆以前也好还是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.28,0:03:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像就该被她们这么欺负似的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 与其说被讨厌不如说是感觉被怨恨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确　感觉到了敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们刚刚有说到约定对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩　也就是说　
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.46,0:03:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你失去记忆之前和她们约定了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为失去记忆 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果就破坏了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得即使问她们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.16,0:03:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不见得她们就会告诉你真相
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有甚者　会趁你失忆 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.20,0:03:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能告诉你假象 说谎骗你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是隐瞒失忆这件事比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然打工的伙伴虽然也不像坏人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,青梅竹马的shin和toma
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都还不知道是什么样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且　现在还不知道谁对你抱有敌意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.40,0:04:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道从哪就泄露了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道和那些人的约定是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.32,0:04:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是是因为我不守约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使别人受到了伤害 伤了心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　让你担心了 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还没完全好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛　我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,sawa前辈 真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 mine 你也要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人感觉很可信啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈 感觉 不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易觉得顺利了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然危机就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说哪儿不一样还真难说。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.25,0:05:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确　发呆的时候很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这孩子以前也有这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯— 漂亮的圆场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:16.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是有旅行的预备会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.85,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行　那个…　难道　你也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？预备会 所有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.81,0:05:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打工的亲睦旅行 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家之前说好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对 对 之前说shin是应考生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是不能去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会应试学习的效率也会提高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 shin就勉勉强强说去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 就成了全员参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说前辈 完全看不出来你很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3天2夜的信浓旅行 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个状态 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然一下子 难度太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在旅行中 不出差错很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这样 也是恢复记忆的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往积极的方向想想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.70,0:06:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才就一个人在哪咕咕噜噜说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送去3号桌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:06:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.67,0:07:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.84,0:07:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 是shin吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.84,0:07:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.07,0:07:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.60,0:07:21.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是晴天就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨看不见就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.91,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 出主意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.22,0:07:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.97,0:07:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟了 shin也往这里看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你说想看mineme流星群的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先很好的敷衍过这个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 还有什么其他的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不小心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲信越的本周天气预报总体晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:14.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我说了想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.88,0:08:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你学习还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没事了所以才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 kent 你是数学系的研究生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他教你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 事先整理好要问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以不浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次目的在于
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.48,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让零度之羊的工作人员增加友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说了 那么 废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.40,0:09:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家尽情的玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算 撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 竟是不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 让大家觉得奇怪也无可奈可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 要特别注意mine和shin 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.74,0:09:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉她们已经起疑心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了，可以成为你记忆暗示的那个东西 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你去主动问问或许更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 要是能这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.28,0:09:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明说了会加油的 可是完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.19,0:09:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,orion在 我觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 怎么也找不回那些记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信号是红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.78,0:10:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发呆可是很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有过这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夷？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不记得我…了吗    也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.24,0:10:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 以前见过那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉我刚才心绪不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好美的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我是第一次乘坐这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 很不错的地方唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 shin又在看你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么总感觉他好像说什么的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.07,0:11:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道　感觉到你失忆的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.52,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末不是晴空万丈 降水率为0的吗？kent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是半周的预报 天气瞬息万变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是倾盆大雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了，大家 我想这雨很快就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.12,0:12:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不见要停啊 你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过气味知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？气味？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气通过气味就能预测吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不管怎么看 就是不见停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 即使是对我保证一件事情也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,kent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.35,0:12:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.69,0:13:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真像waka说的那样 雨真停了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚说完就停了 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨的味道 是什么样的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.08,0:13:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 我的脸上沾上什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表情像在做白日梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 他这么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 问一下他 你看到的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个 听见雨的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会想起之前去过的庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多漂亮的风铃摆在摊子上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:59.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下小雨的时候 kent把我拉到伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  又是面无表情 记得吗 记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你 去庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么看来 kent这好像没有线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 唉 到现在为止你看到的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是片段 连接不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现的人也是乱七八糟 到底是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 因为是失忆之前经历的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 一边等流星 一边一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团体赛 台式冰球开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 最先的对决shin&toma队 对 kent&Ikki队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,shin 你防我守 这样可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 除此之外没有更好的布局了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有人大声说出了作战计划了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不起我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢  Ikki 很擅长这个游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是乒乓球部的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:17.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是飞镖部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.15,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 动手的游戏都很擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.09,0:15:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不需要作战会议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经决定了 我立案 Ikiki 实施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.26,0:15:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ikiki 不会是 ikki吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绰号 真名 无论哪个 都不合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上干活的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的好随意啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.86,0:15:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.23,0:15:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 俩对准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.03,0:16:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意露破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.53,0:16:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,kent&Ikki 队胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.05,0:16:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 Ikki 也太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 kent的大胆的作战计划也相当了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.98,0:16:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 动手的游戏没胜算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 打牌 玩扑克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 不过 先说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是无论什么动手的游戏都很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.52,0:16:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑克也是 另一种意思的动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经 觉得不会赢Ikki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 来了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 谢谢 orion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 我什么也没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一个人的话 肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有orion在 帮了我很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是和你在一起 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这样一来 就和你一起有许多的经历 很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,orion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 下一个就轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,mineme流星群 据说看到这个流星群的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在心里留下美好的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.79,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今晚留下好的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 还有多远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:17:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.63,0:18:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,台式冰球太卖力了 用光了力气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 多亏了你赢了那个店长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我自己也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长的球 半路就不见了 难为你能打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那 那是 瞎蒙的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎样 很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,shin
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累坏了啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 手拿来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.61,0:18:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我有想问的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在两个人独处很糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道会问什么 必须糊弄过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.07,0:19:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那。。。那个 不追上去 大家会担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没关系 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了。。。人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈。。哈哈 没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,替你送过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还没呢 因为 那个人在这 哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.46,0:20:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,shin
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.65,0:20:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经10点了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？八月一日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡太久了 你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 发什么呆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来叫醒你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.88,0:21:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
